OL,3,CFlu surge leaves patients and
OL,4,Cambulances waiting at A&E
OL,6,FITV News Meridian's Wesley Smith was
OL,7,Fgiven access to Royal Berkshire
OL,8,FHospital's A&E to see how staff are
OL,9,Fcoping.
OL,11,FAs we brace for a freezing weekend and
OL,12,Fa surge in cases of flu, bosses at
OL,13,FReading's Royal Berkshire Hospital are
OL,14,Fwarning people to only attend A&E in
OL,15,Fan emergency.
OL,17,FThere's been little let-up in demand
OL,18,Fsince mid-December with an influx of
OL,19,Fpatients on Friday morning (January 3)
OL,20,Fleaving the hospital under extra
OL,21,Fpressure.
