OL,3,CFlu surge leaves patients and
OL,4,Cambulances waiting at A&E
OL,6,FSome patients had to wait for longer
OL,7,Fthan the target of four hours and
OL,8,Fambulances were queuing outside.
OL,10,FWith temperatures set to plunge over
OL,11,Fthe next few days people are being
OL,12,Furged to prepare and consider other
OL,13,Foptions before heading to the
OL,14,FEmergency Department.
OL,16,FBy mid-morning staff at the Royal
OL,17,FBerkshire Hospital A&E already had
OL,18,Fmore patients than beds.
