OL,3,CFlu surge leaves patients and
OL,4,Cambulances waiting at A&E
OL,6,F"We've got 31 patients waiting to be
OL,7,Fadmitted to the hospital, that's 31
OL,8,Fbeds I can't use because I have
OL,9,Fpatients in them, and I've got eight
OL,10,Fambulances queuing outside," said
OL,11,FEmergency Medicine Consultant, Omar
OL,12,FNafousi.
OL,14,F"I've got 25 patients waiting at the
OL,15,Fmoment to be seen by us and the wait
OL,16,Ffor us to see patients is only about
OL,17,Fan hour and a half, so my team is
OL,18,Fdoing a fantastic job trying to stay
OL,19,Fon the waits."
