OL,3,CFlu surge leaves patients and
OL,4,Cambulances waiting at A&E
OL,6,F"But my struggle is getting patients
OL,7,Fin, off an ambulance into my
OL,8,Fdepartment so I can do what I need to
OL,9,Fmake them better and discharge them or
OL,10,Fadmit them."
OL,12,FAnd he predicts it will remains busy
OL,13,Ffor at least another month or two.
OL,15,FThe NHS says it's seeing three times
OL,16,Fthe number of flu cases as last year,
OL,17,Fwith 5,000 patients admitted to
OL,18,Fhospital nationwide at the end of last
OL,19,Fweek.
