OL,3,CFlu surge leaves patients and
OL,4,Cambulances waiting at A&E
OL,6,FHospital Chief Executive, Steve
OL,7,FMcManus, admits it's putting a strain
OL,8,Fon waiting time targets.
OL,10,F"So it does fluctuate and I'd like to
OL,11,Fapologise for those extended waits
OL,12,Fthat some patients will have. We have
OL,13,Fto prioritise those patients that have
OL,14,Fgot the greatest need or have the
OL,15,Fgreatest vulnerability," said Mr
OL,16,FMcManus.
