OL,3,CFlu surge leaves patients and
OL,4,Cambulances waiting at A&E
OL,6,F"In the middle part of December we
OL,7,Fwere seeing around 20 to 30 people
OL,8,Fwith flu admitted each day, we're now
OL,9,Fseeing about 50 patients with flu in
OL,10,Four beds."
OL,12,F"But again, we're encouraging people
OL,13,Fwho are experiencing those severe
OL,14,Frespiratory illnesses, if you need our
OL,15,Fsupport, the emergency team here at
OL,16,Fthe Royal Berks are ready to support
OL,17,Fand help."
