OL,3,CFlu surge leaves patients and
OL,4,Cambulances waiting at A&E
OL,6,FLate this afternoon the hospital
OL,7,Frequested visitors to wear masks and
OL,8,Favoid coming in if aware of flu-like
OL,9,Fsymptoms.
OL,11,FAnnouncing plans for reforming social
OL,12,Fcare today, The Health Secretary, Wes
OL,13,FStreeting, says his plans should
OL,14,Feventually help ease A&E backlogs.
OL,16,F"As well as our 10 year plan for the
OL,17,FNHS and all the reform we're doing
OL,18,Fthere, we also need to reform our
OL,19,Fsocial care," said Mr Streeting.
