OL,3,CFlu surge leaves patients and
OL,4,Cambulances waiting at A&E
OL,6,F"One of the reasons we why we see A&E
OL,7,Fdepartments so busy is because we
OL,8,Fcan't get people out of hospital beds
OL,9,Fout into the community because of a
OL,10,Flack of social care."
OL,12,FIn the short term, with an amber
OL,13,Fweather alert for parts of Oxfordshire
OL,14,Fand Buckinghamshire this weekend,
OL,15,Fpeople are advised to be prepared and
OL,16,Ftry to avoid using Emergency
OL,17,FDepartments unless absolutely
OL,18,Fnecessary.
